audioanalyze.whatitdoes: transcribes audio/video to text, supports audio and video

caption.whatitdoes: Adds a caption to an image, supports images and videos

riodejaneiro.whatitdoes: Adds a Rio De Janeiro instagram filter over an image, supports images and videos

speechbubble.whatitdoes: adds a speechbubble on top of an image/video, supports images and videos

toaudio.whatitdoes: Converts a video to a mp3, supports videos

togif.whatitdoes: Converts a video to a gif, supports videos

toimage.whatitdoes: Converts all video frames to images, supports videos
